pageProduct.name: Scholl Gel Toe Separator Pain Relief and Protection
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Soft gel technology. Immediate relief from painful pressure and rubbing. Clear and discreet. Protects sore areas between the toes.

Scholl Gel Toe Separators provide relief from pain and soreness between the toes.


- Ideal for sore spots, blisters and corns between the toes.


- Slim, soft and comfortable for optimum comfort.


- Washable.

Boxed Contents: 2 Large 1 Small

Size: 3 Pack

Warnings

KEEP OUT OF THE REACH OF CHILDREN. Avoid using on cracked or broken skin. If you suffer from diabetes or poor circulation, consult your healthcare professional before use. If seal on pack is broken, do not use.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

Please SEEK ADVICE before use if you have diabetes as your foot condition may require treatment by a healthcare professional.

Directions

Place between the toes with the long edge to the top. Remove overnight. Washing Instructions: Hand wash with mild soap and lukewarm water. Rinse thoroughly then leave to dry naturally.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool, dry place out of direct sunlight.

Storage Temperature: Store below 25°C.

Washable?: true
